ATTRIBUTION / АТРИБУЦИЯ

This product includes work derived from the Anthropic "knowledge-work-plugins"
project — https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins — Copyright
Anthropic, licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

31 of the 34 skills are localized adaptations (translated into Russian and modified
for the Russian small-business, tax and legal context — connectors, USN/VAT/contributions,
Civil & Labor Code, currency) of the upstream "small-business" plugin. The files have
been changed; each derived SKILL.md carries an in-file notice.

ORIGINAL WORK / ОРИГИНАЛЬНОЕ (not derived from the project above):
  - skills/counterparty-guard      — проверка контрагента по ИНН (INN counterparty check)
  - skills/tax-calendar-proactive  — проактивный налоговый штурман УСН (USN tax navigator)
  - skills/cross-source-verify     — движок круговой сверки (based on knowledge-work-plugins/enterprise-search)
